OL,3,CSchool leaders' union launches legal
OL,4,Caction against Ofsted
OL,6,FA school leaders' union say it is
OL,7,Ftaking legal action against Ofsted
OL,8,Fover the potential impact of their
OL,9,Finspection proposals on the mental
OL,10,Fhealth of headteachers and school
OL,11,Fstaff.
OL,13,FThe National Association of Head
OL,14,FTeachers (NAHT) issued a claim to the
OL,15,FHigh Court for judicial review on
OL,16,FFriday as it says that adequate
OL,17,Fconsultation has not been conducted
OL,18,Fregarding the education watchdog's
OL,19,Freport card plans.
