OL,3,CSchool leaders' union launches legal
OL,4,Caction against Ofsted
OL,6,FThe claim comes ahead of the NAHT's
OL,7,Fannual conference in Harrogate, North
OL,8,FYorkshire, this weekend.
OL,10,FUnder Ofsted's plans, which were set
OL,11,Fout in a consultation in February,
OL,12,Fschools in England could be graded
OL,13,Facross eight to 10 areas of a
OL,14,Fprovision using a colour-coded five-
OL,15,Fpoint scale.
OL,17,FThey would receive ratings, from the
OL,18,Fred "causing concern" to orange
OL,19,F"attention needed", through the green
OL,20,Fshades of "secure", "strong" and
OL,21,F"exemplary" for each area of practice.
