OL,3,CSchool leaders' union launches legal
OL,4,Caction against Ofsted
OL,6,FThe NAHT has said Ofsted's report card
OL,7,Fproposals involve an increased number
OL,8,Fof graded sub-judgments, which school
OL,9,Fleaders fear will only increase high-
OL,10,Fstakes accountability and pressure.
OL,12,FA motion to be debated at the NAHT
OL,13,Fannual conference on Saturday calls
OL,14,Ffor the introduction of Ofsted report
OL,15,Fcards as a measure of school
OL,16,Faccountability to be "opposed".
