OL,3,CSchool leaders' union launches legal
OL,4,Caction against Ofsted
OL,6,FThe motion, on which conference
OL,7,Fdelegates will vote, calls for all
OL,8,F"legal and industrial options" to be
OL,9,Fexplored fully to protect the mental
OL,10,Fand physical health and wellbeing of
OL,11,Fschool leaders and staff.
OL,13,FLast year, the government announced
OL,14,Fthat headline Ofsted grades for
OL,15,Foverall effectiveness for schools in
OL,16,FEngland would be scrapped.
OL,18,FPreviously, Ofsted awarded one of four
OL,19,Fsingle-phrase inspection judgments:
OL,20,Foutstanding, good, requires
OL,21,Fimprovement and inadequate.
