OL,3,CSchool leaders' union launches legal
OL,4,Caction against Ofsted
OL,6,FThe move came after Ofsted faced
OL,7,Fcriticism after the death of
OL,8,Fheadteacher Ruth Perry.
OL,10,FMrs Perry took her own life in January
OL,11,F2023 after an Ofsted report downgraded
OL,12,Fher Caversham Primary School in
OL,13,FReading, Berkshire, from the highest
OL,14,Fto the lowest overall effectiveness
OL,15,Frating over safeguarding concerns.
