OL,3,CSchool leaders' union launches legal
OL,4,Caction against Ofsted
OL,6,FOn Monday, Julia Waters, Mrs Perry's
OL,7,Fsister, joined education professionals
OL,8,Fin an open letter to Education
OL,9,FSecretary Bridget Phillipson calling
OL,10,Ffor proposed changes to Ofsted
OL,11,Finspections to be delayed.
OL,13,FIn a fresh statement, Prof Waters
OL,14,Fsaid: "I share the frustration of
OL,15,Fheadteachers. Everyone agrees that
OL,16,Fschools and teachers should be
OL,17,Faccountable for the quality of the
OL,18,Feducation they provide. But this new
OL,19,Fsystem, proposed for itself by Ofsted,
OL,20,Fcould be worse than the flawed and
OL,21,Fdangerous process it replaces.
OL,26,@vD@GOU
