OL,3,CSchool leaders' union launches legal
OL,4,Caction against Ofsted
OL,6,F"We have enough evidence from repeated
OL,7,Finquiries and other national systems
OL,8,Fthat show what might work better for
OL,9,Fpupils, parents, and teachers as a
OL,10,Fsystem of school inspection in
OL,11,FEngland."
OL,13,FPaul Whiteman, general secretary of
OL,14,Fthe NAHT, said: "Somehow the focus on
OL,15,Fschool leader mental health and
OL,16,Fwellbeing has got lost along the way
OL,17,Fduring Ofsted's consultation process.
