OL,3,CSchool leaders' union launches legal
OL,4,Caction against Ofsted
OL,6,F"We must not forget that the catalyst
OL,7,Ffor these changes was the tragic death
OL,8,Fof Ruth Perry and widespread
OL,9,Facceptance that the inspection regime
OL,10,Fwas placing school leaders under
OL,11,Fintolerable pressure.
OL,13,F"However, there appears to have been
OL,14,Fvery little thought given to the
OL,15,Fimpact on the wellbeing of school
OL,16,Fleaders in the drawing up of these
OL,17,Fplans and the consultation that
OL,18,Ffollowed.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
