OL,3,CSchool leaders' union launches legal
OL,4,Caction against Ofsted
OL,6,F"School leaders are deeply concerned
OL,7,Fthat the new report cards could result
OL,8,Fin an even worse system than before,
OL,9,Fwith potentially disastrous impact on
OL,10,Fworkload, wellbeing and retention.
OL,12,F"We have tried engaging with Ofsted
OL,13,Fand explaining this, but so far these
OL,14,Fconcerns have fallen largely on deaf
OL,15,Fears.
OL,17,F"We have been left with little choice
OL,18,Fother than to pursue this action."
