OL,3,CSchool leaders' union launches legal
OL,4,Caction against Ofsted
OL,6,FAn Ofsted spokeswoman said:
OL,7,F"Supporting the mental health of those
OL,8,Fwe inspect is an important part of the
OL,9,Fdevelopment of our proposals and we
OL,10,Fare already hearing positive feedback
OL,11,Fthrough our inspection tests.
OL,13,F"Our legal team have responded
OL,14,Frobustly to NAHT.
OL,16,F"Their suggested claims are plainly
OL,17,Funtenable.
OL,19,F"If legal action is launched, we will
OL,20,Fresist and seek costs."
